<h1>[Boilerplate] <%= email.subject %></h1>

<p>Hi <%= user.name %>, we got a request to reset your password associated to your email <%= user.email %>.</p>

<p>Use the verification code below to reset your password.</p>
  
<p><strong><%= user.resetShortToken %></strong></p>

<p>If you didn't request this change please let us know by following <a href='mailto:boilerplate.js@gmail.com?subject=I did not ask to reset my password&body=Someone unauthorized sent this reset password request.'>this link</a>.</p>

